IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. DB2SELT.
ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA END-EXEC.
01  WS-EMP-NO        PIC 9(06).
01  WS-EMP-NAME      PIC X(30).
01  WS-SQLCODE       PIC S9(9) COMP.
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    MOVE 100001 TO WS-EMP-NO.
    EXEC SQL
        SELECT EMP_NAME
          INTO :WS-EMP-NAME
          FROM EMPLOYEE
         WHERE EMP_NO = :WS-EMP-NO
    END-EXEC.
    MOVE SQLCODE TO WS-SQLCODE.
    IF WS-SQLCODE = 0
       DISPLAY 'EMP NAME: ' WS-EMP-NAME
    ELSE
       DISPLAY 'DB2 ERROR, SQLCODE=' WS-SQLCODE
    END-IF.
    STOP RUN.
